        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In macOS, the default implementation of this method calls the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "preferredSizeOfLayer:"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method of its layout manager—that is, the object in its "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/calayer/1410749-layoutmanager"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. If that object does not exist or does not implement that method, this method returns the size of the layer’s current "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/quartzcore/calayer/1410915-bounds"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " rectangle mapped into the coordinate space of its "
            },
